Rating: 4
This is one of my all time favorite recipes. I have always substituted a high quality black bean sauce which is easier to find than the salted black beans. Don't be put off by the sound of oyster sauce (I know that didn't sound good to some of my friends!). The fragrance of the ginger, garlic, etc. is divine.